    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a new adventure! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. Whether you're headed to work or out for a weekend trip, this car handles beautifully and still looks great in the driveway. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it's ready to hit the road with you today. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it feels!",
