    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused BMW E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 engine. This high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and delivers a linear torque curve up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring precise damping across varying surfaces. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its status, the mechanical integrity and powertrain calibration remain sharp.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
