    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and daily usability, maintained with a focus on longevity. The exterior finish presents beautifully, retaining a high gloss; while there are a few minor road-pebble chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, the body is straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the interior smells fresh and has never been smoked in. The upholstery is in excellent shape with only light bolster wear on the driver's side, and all power features\u2014including the sunroof, heated seats, and infotainment system\u2014operate perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs smoothly, backed by a complete folder of service receipts. Recent work includes a fresh oil service and a new set of premium all-season tires. The transmission shifts crisply, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. This is a turn-key car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 31500.0,
