      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years\u2014perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways! It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
