    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced double VANOS system, addressing critical platform vulnerabilities. The chassis remains tight with updated control arm bushings, providing the communicative steering feel these cars are known for. While the exterior shows honest wear typical of a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust with a functional M Variable Differential Lock and a free-revving induction note. A superb choice for the purist seeking performance over concours perfection.",
